    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OUTL1NED is a manic <i>One-Dimensional</i> arcade shooter where you last as long as you can while enjoying a colourful lightshow in the background.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even though enemies can only come from <strong>2 intense directions</strong> rather than <strong>360 flaccid degrees</strong>, you will have to focus to keep the pressure at bay and manage which direction needs your attention. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be challenged to manage your constantly-regenerating ammo and collect a variety of diverse <strong>upgrades</strong> as you go in order to last as long as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle a <strong>variety of colour-coordinated enemy types</strong> that will vary in speed, health, and visibility that will force you to make tough decisions as they close in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies aren't the only danger as you will occasionally pick up <strong>debuffs</strong> that will obscure your vision and change up how you see the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete to get the highest score globally on the <strong>global leaderboard</strong>.</p>",
